0430\\u0442\\u0435\\u043b\\u044c\\u043d\\u0430\\u044f \\u043a\\u043e\\u043c\\u0430\\u043d\\u0434\\u0430 \\u043c\\u0435\\u0441\\u0442\\u043d\\u044b\\u0445 \\u0433\\u0435\\u0440\\u043e\\u0435\\u0432 \\u0438\\u0437 REST \\u043f\\u043e\\u0441\\u0442\\u0440\\u043e\\u0438\\u0442 \\u0442\\u0443\\u0442 \\u043a\\u043e\\u043b\\u043e\\u0434\\u0435\\u0446. \\u042d\\u0442\\u0438 \\u043b\\u044e\\u0434\\u0438 \\u0440\\u0430\\u0431\\u043e\\u0442\\u0430\\u044e\\u0442 29 \\u0438\\u0437 30 \\u0434\\u043d\\u0435\\u0439 \\u0432 \\u043c\\u0435\\u0441\\u044f\\u0446. \\n\\u041f\\u043e\\u0441\\u043c\\u043e\\u0442\\u0440\\u0438\\u0442\\u0435 \\u0432\\u0438\\u0434\\u0435\\u043e \\u043f\\u043e \\u0441\\u0441\\u044b\\u043b\\u043a\\u0435 \\u0432 \\u0431\\u0438\\u043e \\u0447\\u0442\\u043e\\u0431\\u044b \\u043f\\u043e\\u043d\\u044f\\u0442\\u044c \\u0432\\u0441\\u0451 \\u043e\\u0431 \\u043e\\u0440\\u0433\\u0430\\u043d\\u0438\\u0437\\u0430\\u0446\\u0438\\u0438\",\"from\":{\"username\":\"muradosmann\",\"profile_picture\":\"https:\\/\\/instagram.ffru6-1.fna.fbcdn.net\\/v\\/t51.2885-19\\/s150x150\\/67738325_702894650134555_1234862196349992960_n.jpg?_nc_ht=instagram.ffru6-1.fna.fbcdn.net&_nc_ohc=mosp33XmnqMAX8FMEEq&oh=abbff6c477ddff7243e62f53f7559975&oe=5EC3FB1D\",\"id\":\"6281714\",\"full_name\":\"MURAD OSMANN\",\"counts\":{\"media\":581,\"followed_by\":4064622,\"follows\":842}}},\"type\":\"video\",\"id\":\"2000176685263020809_6281714\",\"code\":\"BvCDhkNHuMJ\",\"user\":{\"username\":\"muradosmann\",\"profile_picture\":\"https:\\/\\/instagram.ffru6-1.fna.fbcdn.net\\/v\\/t51.2885-19\\/s150x150\\/67738325_702894650134555_1234862196349992960_n.jpg?_nc_ht=instagram.ffru6-1.fna.fbcdn.net&_nc_ohc=mosp33XmnqMAX8FMEEq&oh=abbff6c477ddff7243e62f53f7559975&oe=5EC3FB1D\",\"id\":\"6281714\",\"full_name\":\"MURAD OSMANN\",\"counts\":{\"media\":581,\"followed_by\":4064622,\"follows\":842}}},{\"attribution\":null,\"video_url\":null,\"tags\":[\"followmeto\"],\"location\":{\"name\":\"Ethiopia\",\"id\":\"567942857\"},\"comments\":{\"count\":255,\"data\":[{\"created_time\":1565354835,\"text\":\"Wow! How shallow can one be? Totally inappropriate...I feel sorry for you not realizing how many shades of wrong this pic is...\",\"from\":{\"username\":\"gyristroula.travelunusual\",\"profile_picture\":\"https:\\/\\/instagram.ffru6-1.fna.fbcdn.net\\/v\\/t51.2885-19\\/s150x150\\/18299595_1885441651736897_8918282054345424896_a.jpg?_nc_ht=instagram.ffru6-1.fna.fbcdn.net&_nc_ohc=jaYD9GSgxSkAX-ZXSZL&oh=6ac67078a7753572a7f1346ab10308bc&oe=5EC44325\",\"id\":\"5362379785\"}},{\"created_time\":1569188097,\"text\":\"@fio97139 ils ont travers\\u00e9 le monde de long en large mais c\\u2019est quand ils arrivent en \\u00c9thiopie qu\\u2019ils parlent de charit\\u00e9. O\\u00f9 sont les magnifiques paysages de l\\u2019Afrique? Non c\\u2019est l\\u2019Afrique = pauvret\\u00e9. Il n\\u2019y avait pas d\\u2019enfants affam\\u00e9s au Kazakhstan ou en Chine.\",\"from\":{\"username\":\"pheebie_ink\",\"profile_picture\":\"https:\\/\\/instagram.ffru6-1.fna.fbcdn.net\\/v\\/t51.2885-19\\/s150x150\\/15251661_224646234628175_8868627915961532416_a.jpg?_nc_ht=instagram.ffru6-1.fna.fbcdn.net&_nc_ohc=zTlII-fz5ywAX_vPiX-&oh=42fc1444cd2d75b0310995244daabf8e&oe=5EC38363\",\"id\":\"476065285\"}},{\"created_time\":1575394077,\"text\":\"White Saviors\\ud83d\\udc4f\",\"from\":{\"username\":\"alexad0\",\"profile_picture\":\"https:\\/\\/instagram.ffru6-1.fna.fbcdn.net\\/v\\/t51.2885-19\\/s150x150\\/51668777_549063775606083_8486487027615793152_n.jpg?_nc_ht=instagram.ffru6-1.fna.fbcdn.net&_nc_ohc=FId0X_rvDTgAX8CA9z7&oh=31f5d4d9508e2824be77e3bf7775445e&oe=5EC4C26F\",\"id\":\"205288826\"}},{\"created_time\":1575647812,\"text\":\"@quiet6.8\",\"from\":{\"username\":\"sarahmichellechafe\",\"profile_picture\":\"https:\\/\\/instagram.ffru6-1.fna.fbcdn.net\\/v\\/t51.2885-19\\/s150x150\\/88883277_539129686743018_4964168396657655808_n.jpg?_nc_ht=instagram.ffru6-1.fna.fbcdn.net&_nc_ohc=VlE3tp9P1EwAX-AJUhp&oh=49c301cc7cc7b4e9b618dadb95cfeed1&oe=5EC2CA32\",\"id\":\"54322306\"}}]},\"filter\":null,\"created_time\":1552581828,\"link\":\"https:\\/\\/www.instagram.com\\/p\\/Bu_vEMrB0Y4\\/\",\"likes\":{\"count\":59103,\"data\":[]},\"images\":{\"low_resolution\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/instagram.ffru6-1.fna.fbcdn.net\\/v\\/t51.2885-15\\/e35\\/s320x320\\/54512550_550606765450562_2953406746380368915_n.jpg?_nc_ht=instagram.ffru6-1.fna.fbcdn.net&_nc_cat=102&_nc_ohc=QkTwvcSWDWcAX-zoxAQ&oh=d2c0e3cb5b7d8816c7e0f65ecc1d9a6e&oe=5EC3605B\",\"width\":320,\"height\":320},\"thumbnail\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/instagram.ffru6-1.fna.fbcdn.net\\/v\\/t51.2885-15\\/e35\\/s150x150\\/54512550_550606765450562_2953406746380368915_n.jpg?_nc_ht=instagram.ffru6-1.fna.fbcdn.net&_nc_cat=102&_nc_ohc=QkTwvcSWDWcAX-zoxAQ&oh=eafd0061be4a2c3402759a14bc16a59f&oe=5EC1BCAB\",\"width\":150,\"height\":150},\"standard_resolution\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/instagram.ffru6-1.fna.fbcdn.net\\/v\\/t51.2885-15\\/sh0.08\\/e35\\/s640x640\\/54512550_550606765450562_2953406746380368915_n.jpg?_nc_ht=instagram.ffru6-1.fna.fbcdn.net&_nc_cat=102&_nc_ohc=QkTwvcSWDWcAX-zoxAQ&oh=7d61ced342fb8d536bf5fe618d4ed45b&oe=5EC18B8E\",\"width\":640,\"height\":640},\"__original\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/instagram.ffru6-1.fna.fbcdn.net\\/v\\/t51.2885-15\\/e35\\/54512550_550606765450562_2953406746380368915_n.jpg?_nc_ht=instagram.ffru6-1.fna.fbcdn.net&_nc_cat=102&_nc_ohc=QkTwvcSWDWcAX-zoxAQ&oh=22cc49282fab9149f7fda7af8bb3a5fc&oe=5EC24FE9\",\"width\":1080,\"height\":1080}},\"users_in_photo\":null,\"caption\":{\"created_time\":1552581828,\"text\":\"#followmeto @charitywater with @natalyosmann . We were big fans of @charitywater before coming to Ethiopia, but after the trip, where we saw what impact their work has on local communities we trust them 100%. Here we are at the site that doesn\\u2019t have an access to clean water yet. Women would walk 2-4 hours and wait in line with hundreds of other women at this pond. Even though the water looks clean it is highly contaminated with animal waste, worms, and diseases. They would repeat this route 3-4 times a day carrying these  25l Jerry cans. For those who follow our stories - you have seen us repeating their route and it is very very exhausting. \\nWhile Charity:water raises awareness and funds, their local partners drill through bedrock, protect springs and mobilise communities everyday. Their local partner in Ethiopia is REST (Relief Society of Tigray) and they have more than a thousand Ethiopian staff members. All of them are heroes. This village will have access to clean water next time REST and Charity:water come back - which should be within this year. I will tell you more about REST in the later posts.\\n\\u274d\\u274d\\u274d\\u274d\\u274d\\u274d\\u274d\\u274d\\u274d\\u274d\\u274d\\u274d\\u274d\\u274d\\u274d\\u274d\\u274d\\u274d\\u274d\\u274d\\u274d\\u274d\\n\\u261d\\ufe0fPlease check out the video about @scottharrison in my bio and if it affects you the same way it affected us - then join us in achieving the goal to give access to clean water to people of Ethiopia. Link in bio\\u261d\\ufe0f\\n\\u274d\\u274d\\u274d\\u274d\\u274d\\u274d\\u274d\\u274d\\u274d\\u274d\\u274d\\u274d\\u274d\\u274d\\u274d\\u274d\\u274d\\u274d\\u274d\\u274d\\u274d\\u274d\",\"from\":{\"username\":\"muradosmann\",\"profile_picture\":\"https:\\/\\/instagram.ffru6-1.fna.fbcdn.net\\/v\\/t51.2885-19\\/s150x150\\/67738325_702894650134555_1234862196349992960_n.jpg?_nc_ht=instagram.ffru6-1.fna.fbcdn.net&_nc_ohc=mosp33XmnqMAX8FMEEq&oh=abbff6c477ddff7243e62f53f7559975&oe=5EC3FB1D\",\"id\":\"6281714\",\"full_name\":\"MURAD OSMANN\",\"counts\":{\"media\":581,\"followed_by\":4064622,\"follows\":842}}},\"type\":\"carousel\",\"id\":\"1999523756246517304_6281714\",\"code\":\"Bu_vEMrB0Y4\",\"user\":{\"username\":\"muradosmann\",\"profile_picture\":\"https:\\/\\/instagram.ffru6-1.fna.fbcdn.net\\/v\\/t51.2885-19\\/s150x150\\/67738325_702894650134555_1234862196349992960_n.jpg?_nc_ht=instagram.ffru6-1.fna.fbcdn.net&_nc_ohc=mosp33XmnqMAX8F