\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/studentfilmmakers\" class=\"reviewer-name\">StudentFilmmakers <small>(studentfilmmakers)</small></a> <span class=\"review-date\">11 июля, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I had it set up free and thought I needed to just use the paid feature to add an IP to see what login and logout looked like so I got the paid version. However, when you load the paid version and the templates it removes the free templates and set\'s up a whole new workflow that includes building your template and saving it to a template file and then activating it. It put my site online so everyone can see it under construction and this it was not easy to get it back under construction. There was a bug that would not put my site back under the under construction. Finally went back to the free version and have not heard from support.</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:126:\"Super-easy to use Under Construction Page, Maintenance Mode &amp; Coming Soon Page. Enable Under Construction Mode in seconds!\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:71:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/under-construction-page.3.75.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:40:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:76:\"https://ps.w.org/under-construction-page/assets/screenshot-1.gif?rev=1840052\";s:7:\"caption\";s:74:\"Build an under construction page in less than a minute with over 30 themes\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:76:\"https://ps.w.org/under-construction-page/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=1840052\";s:7:\"caption\";s:29:\"Under Construction Text theme\";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:76:\"https://ps.w.org/under-construction-page/assets/screenshot-3.png?rev=1840052\";s:7:\"caption\";s:18:\"Mad Designer theme\";}i:4;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:76:\"https://ps.w.org/under-construction-page/assets/screenshot-4.png?rev=1840052\";s:7:\"caption\";s:16:\"Plain Text theme\";}i:5;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:76:\"https://ps.w