;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/markisparki\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5acd78849f60aaf750820cb024f83944?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5acd78849f60aaf750820cb024f83944?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/markisparki\" class=\"reviewer-name\">markisparki</a> <span class=\"review-date\">11 марта, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">For this kind of plugin, I am looking for the following:\nSimple, straigh-forward, light and, of course, that it works. \nScore 4 stars for this incredible plugin. Actually, let\'s make that 5 as it is free!\nInside 20 seconds I am now HSTS with all my last remaining mixed content being forced to HTTPS whilst I track it all down.\nRecommended.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">easy easy easy</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"review