itors will visit you without seeing \"Not Secure\" in the url that will probably make them nervous, guess what.. WP Force SSL is all you need. Easy, one click plugin to rule them all! All your pages will show padlock that will show security and you will gain trust and credibility! Thank you for the developer of this amazing plugin! More power to you!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Fantastic!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/orapoi\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e064e7d592232c1c3a4b7c6a0636713c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e064e7d592232c1c3a4b7c6a0636713c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/orapoi\" class=\"reviewer-name\">orapoi</a> <span class=\"review-date\">14 февраля, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This thing just works, which cannot always be said for the fancier plugins.  Well done!</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:86:\"Enable SSL with 1 click! Add an SSL certificate &amp; WP Force SSL to redirect&hellip;\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:60:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/wp-force-ssl.1.55.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:2:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\